&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;前言&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Countless programmers have learned C++ from previous editions of C++ Primer. &lt;cite&gt;During that time&lt;sup id="fnref:1"&gt;&lt;a href="#fn:1" class="footnote-ref" role="doc-noteref"&gt;1&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/cite&gt;, C++ has &lt;cite&gt;matured&lt;sup id="fnref:2"&gt;&lt;a href="#fn:2" class="footnote-ref" role="doc-noteref"&gt;2&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/cite&gt; greatly: Its focus, and that of its programming community, has &lt;cite&gt;widened&lt;sup id="fnref:3"&gt;&lt;a href="#fn:3" class="footnote-ref" role="doc-noteref"&gt;3&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/cite&gt; from looking mostly &lt;cite&gt;efficiency&lt;sup id="fnref:4"&gt;&lt;a href="#fn:4" class="footnote-ref" role="doc-noteref"&gt;4&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/cite&gt; to devoting more attention to programmer efficiency.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;难以计数的c++程序员通过上一个版本的c++ primer学会了c++。而在这段时间里，c++变得更成熟了: 语言本身和它的编程社区的关注点，从主要关注的机器执行效率扩大到了更多的关开发效率。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In 2011, the C++ standards committee&lt;sub&gt;/kəˈmɪti/ n. 委员会&lt;/sub&gt; &lt;cite&gt;issued&lt;sup id="fnref:5"&gt;&lt;a href="#fn:5" class="footnote-ref" role="doc-noteref"&gt;5&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/cite&gt; a &lt;cite&gt;major&lt;sup id="fnref:6"&gt;&lt;a href="#fn:6" class="footnote-ref" role="doc-noteref"&gt;6&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/cite&gt; revision to the ISO C++ standard. This &lt;cite&gt;revised&lt;sup id="fnref:7"&gt;&lt;a href="#fn:7" class="footnote-ref" role="doc-noteref"&gt;7&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/cite&gt; standard is latest step in C++&amp;rsquo;s evolution and continues the &lt;cite&gt;emphasis&lt;sup id="fnref:8"&gt;&lt;a href="#fn:8" class="footnote-ref" role="doc-noteref"&gt;8&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/cite&gt; on programmer efficiency. The &lt;cite&gt;primary&lt;sup id="fnref:9"&gt;&lt;a href="#fn:9" class="footnote-ref" role="doc-noteref"&gt;9&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/cite&gt; goals of the new standard are to&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>